transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, this is Viagra.

Speaker 2: Hi, I'm calling to cancel my prescription.

Speaker 1: All right, let me pull your prescription here.

Speaker 2: What is the phone number that you use for your account?

Speaker 1: 310-995-0812.

Speaker 2: I don't have any account under that number. You may have used a different one.

Speaker 1: Okay, we'll try 562-233-9418.

Speaker 2: There we go, Mr. Gilbert Estrada.

Speaker 1: Correct.

Speaker 2: All right, so I see that you have a Rescoblue VIP account for Viagra.

Speaker 1: You have a prescription for Viagra 100 mg from Dr. Green, 10 tablets every 30 days.

Speaker 2: You just don't need your refill as often?

Speaker 1: No, I just don't need it anymore.

Speaker 2: Okay, I have the pharmacy pausing everything. You can order as needed. Monthly is not required.

Speaker 1: No, that's okay. I'd just like to cancel it.

Speaker 2: All right, just keep in mind, if something changes, because I'm cancelling the doctor consultation,

Speaker 1: you're going to have a different price because, of course, they're going to have to refinance a new doctor evaluation,

Speaker 2: which could have an impact on your price in the future if you try to reorder.

Speaker 1: That's why they offer to pause.

Speaker 2: I'm cancelling the doctor prescription and the new VIP account.

Speaker 1: All right, Mr. Estrada, I cancelled everything. Consultation cancelled and account is cancelled.

Speaker 2: Okay, you're all set.

Speaker 1: Can I get a confirmation sent to me?

Speaker 2: Yeah, I can have a confirmation number over the phone if you like, if you have a pen.

Speaker 1: Yes, please.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you so much.

Speaker 1: All right, you're all set. Bye-bye.
